172700             GO                      TO     520-S-END-TRANS.
172800
172900     END-TRANSACTION            NO-AUDIT  PRODRDSDS
173000        ON   EXCEPTION
173100             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T690/DB : END ERROR TDBDETRAN"
173200             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU   140-S-ERRODB
173300             CALL    SYSTEM          DMTERMINATE.
173400
173500     MOVE    SPACES                  TO      CH-TRANSACTION.
173600
173700
173800 520-S-END-TRANS.
173900     EXIT.
174000
