174400******************************************************************
174500
174600 540-E-CONV-ERRO-ECRV.
174700
174800     SET     IC1                     TO      1.
174900
175000     SEARCH  TBB-ECRV-ERRO           AT     END
175100             MOVE  207               TO     OUT-RETORNO
175200       WHEN  TBB-ERRO(IC1)           =      IA1
175300             MOVE  TBB-ECRV(IC1)     TO     OUT-RETORNO
175400             GO                      TO     540-S-CONV-ERRO-ECRV.
175500
175600
175700 540-S-CONV-ERRO-ECRV.
