176400
176500 550-E-INCL-PLACDS.
176600
176700
176800
176900     BEGIN-TRANSACTION       NO-AUDIT        PRODRDSDS
177000         ON  EXCEPTION
177100             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T690/DB - ERRO BEGIN-TRANS"
177200             PERFORM 140-E-ERRODB    THRU   140-S-ERRODB
