178600     MOVE    IN01-RT902-MUNIC-VEIC   TO     PLA-MUN-SEDE
178700                                            PLA-MUN-ULTLOC.
178800** INVERTE data recebida da BIN (FT DDMMAAAA)
178900     MOVE    IN01-RT902-DTULTATU     TO     AX-DATA-DDMM4A
179000     MOVE    AX-DDMM4A-DIA           TO     AX-4AMMDD-DIA.
179100     MOVE    AX-DDMM4A-MES           TO     AX-4AMMDD-MES.
179200     MOVE    AX-DDMM4A-ANO           TO     AX-4AMMDD-ANO.
179300     MOVE    AX-DATA-4AMMDD          TO     PLA-DT-CADASTR.
179400     MOVE    0                       TO     PLA-FILLER
179500                                            PLA-SITUACAO.
179600
179700     STORE   PRODPLACDS
179800         ON  EXCEPTION
